_sText:
My second map is inspired by the "aim_ak_colt" map, which is very ugly, but very good. So, i've made a new map, without the m4a1, in a much nicer tarrain. There are four rocks, instead of four "stone blocks", and a little outpost on the top, of to of them. There is also a beautefull lake in the middle of the map.
- Have fun, i hope you will enjoy my map!
